Let’s test our changes.

msgs = ["tell me a joke"]
r, text = openai_chat(mk_msgs(msgs))
text

"Why don't skeletons fight each other?\n\nThey don't have the guts!"



msgs += [r, "tell me another joke that's similar to your first joke"]
r, text = openai_chat(mk_msgs(msgs))
